== Births == * {{ill|Hoen|ja|保延|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1139]] {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Konoe Tennō|ja|近衛天皇|qq=}}, the 76th Emperor of Japan (died [[1155]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1842]] {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Matsumura Junzō|ja|松村淳蔵|qq=}}, a military personnel (died [[1919]]).
== Deaths == * [[Shōkyō]] 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元亨|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1333]] {{ill|June 30|ja|6月30日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Morotoki|ja|北条守時|qq=}}, the 16th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1295]]). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1587]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōmura Sumitada|ja|大村純忠|qq=}}, a Christian daimyō who dispatched the Tenshō mission to Europe (born [[1533]]). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1705]] {{ill|July 8|ja|7月8日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunayoshi|ja|徳川綱吉|qq=}}, the 3rd lord of the Kishū Domain (born [[1665]]).
