== Deaths == * [[Shōkyō]] 2nd year / [[:en:Genkō (1321–1324)|Genkō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1333]] [[:en:June 30|June 30]]) – [[:en:Hōjō Moritoki|Hōjō Morotoki]], the 16th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1295]]). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 15th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1587]] [[:en:June 23|June 23]]) – [[:en:Ōmura Sumitada|Ōmura Sumitada]], a Christian daimyō who dispatched the Tenshō mission to Europe (born [[1533]]). * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1705]] [[:en:July 8|July 8]]) – [[:en:Tokugawa Tsunayoshi|Tokugawa Tsunayoshi]], the 3rd lord of the Kishū Domain (born [[1665]]).
